    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/e9014e093158e1ea9fcc9f8f05a6b382.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/e9014e093158e1ea9fcc9f8f05a6b382.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/e9014e093158e1ea9fcc9f8f05a6b382.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rebel Roar</strong> 是一款充满动作性的卡牌生成器，您可以将动物卡牌与等级进行策略性组合，创建新的反叛战士，并与暴虐的赛皮恩人展开激烈的卡牌战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/4bff341ac2f67c8bece77b812e4d7aad.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/4bff341ac2f67c8bece77b812e4d7aad.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/4bff341ac2f67c8bece77b812e4d7aad.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从隐秘的猫忍者到狡猾的负鼠黑客，领导反抗者对抗压迫性的 XSapiens 公司。在这款惊险刺激的游戏中，解放你的动物伙伴，结成强大的联盟，挑战现状。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/0993e5a291a73931a4598b335a0b3102.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/0993e5a291a73931a4598b335a0b3102.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/0993e5a291a73931a4598b335a0b3102.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过 20 种动物参与您的战斗</h2>探索 5 个不同的家族和 20 多种神奇的动物，每种动物都有自己独特的能力和战斗策略，重新定义战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/ed568d2a8fee61bd635d015dadd767ff.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/ed568d2a8fee61bd635d015dadd767ff.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/ed568d2a8fee61bd635d015dadd767ff.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >释放革命的力量</h2>为您勇敢的动物解锁 20 种等级，巧妙搭配您的卡牌，施展毁灭性的连击，打败您的敌人，改变历史进程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/d7b8b189aab2a2384c2c6e3e13023e7a.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/d7b8b189aab2a2384c2c6e3e13023e7a.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/d7b8b189aab2a2384c2c6e3e13023e7a.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义和主宰 </h2>使用 200 多张反叛贴纸个性化您的游戏机，这些贴纸将把您的英雄变成反抗的象征，让您在与 XSapiens 公司的斗争中获得所需的优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/9bed6e93f6b75f367d67a0766c083f0f.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/9bed6e93f6b75f367d67a0766c083f0f.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/9bed6e93f6b75f367d67a0766c083f0f.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直面命运 </h2>参与史诗般的战斗，最多 3 名英雄对抗 3 名敌人，探索 6 个不同的生物群落，推翻腐败的 XSapiens 帝国。革命已经开始！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/226f0ef2d945518c1e4743f797e0c1ff.poster.avif?t=1756038507\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/226f0ef2d945518c1e4743f797e0c1ff.webm?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062700/extras/226f0ef2d945518c1e4743f797e0c1ff.mp4?t=1756038507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
